{"tid":422197,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【知法犯法】向涉非禮男子勒索2萬 CCB警長被捕停職","createTime":"2017-10-03T00:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T11:12:06.000Z","uid":54733,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce8acd45d837c5abb392e16fdc6920f49b199f6d","tid":422197,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"警務人員知法犯法！商業罪案調查科一名休班警長，約兩個多月前在港鐵太子站發現一名男子涉及一宗非禮案，卻未有將對方拘捕，反知法犯法要求對方給他2萬元以換取不追究案件，事主給警長1萬元後獲放行，其後覺可疑向警方報案，警方翻看現場「天眼」片段後及經深入調查後，昨日(2日)在機場將剛由台灣旅遊返港的警長拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n被捕49歲警長姓張，隸屬商業罪案調查科，事發時休班，他涉嫌勒索及盜竊被通宵扣查，而有人被捕後否認涉案。案發7月13日，男事主在港鐵太子站被張警截停，指他涉及一宗非禮案，要將他帶往旺角警署調查，但有人將事主帶走期間，向事主稱若給他2萬元，便可讓他離去不予追究。消息稱，懷疑事主心虛，討價還價後支付1萬元獲准離去。<br />\n<br />\n但事主返家後覺得事件可疑，翌日向警方報案。警方接報，一度懷疑有人冒警行騙，翻看現場的閉路電視錄影片段，果發現張警與事主同行，惟沒拍攝到事主交錢給對方。警方經過兩個多月調查後，相信張警涉案，但發現他去了台灣旅行及會於昨日返港，遂到機場將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人指涉案警員已被停職，稱警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"fcd11761204642c6ce53e640432fc662ac861ab7","tid":422197,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1506964355_20b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1506964355_20b6.jpg&h=b3427537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ae8bf7ec66c5c98de24b747828e6653f935cb36","tid":422197,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57283934&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57283934%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171003&d=CmemZmFyzWbYnZ7Ld0a%2FVgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=32763a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57283934%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171003&h=5aa98ac8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57283934&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171003</a>"},{"pid":"30ca202e8bd74433e53bc17b5ca6165c57b840bf","tid":422197,"uid":129111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰段真係呃稿費"},{"pid":"ec1de0443d2f74dbacf03dc9d8356a255ed8fc57","tid":422197,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"😂😂😂"},{"pid":"ac5bd661fa91ad277bc68d3979a30fced8fc59de","tid":422197,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:39:08.000Z","msg":"49歲（警長）"},{"pid":"1928f738b32d97c8a8e80cde5e825d7f73039f5d","tid":422197,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾嗰段真係呃稿費</blockquote><br />\n次次有關警察罪行嘅新聞都見到"},{"pid":"14420e69fee0d847f50af4352a7d81e13db87573","tid":422197,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾嗰段真係呃稿費</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d55c62ad936f7a4993e0dc69d603a1ebc5070ae","tid":422197,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾嗰段真係呃稿費</blockquote><br />\n識背 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70c08479cb1160746c0d281f187851ea95fbe43","tid":422197,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978fe7c35428cb73c46608015f9e70ba7be968f9","tid":422197,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"d黑警真係蠢撚到"},{"pid":"e7830